io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.image

Interface DrawableMap

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DynamicImageProxy, StaticImageProxy
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicImage, StaticImage

    public interface DrawableMap
    Holds the map image and functions which call the necessary draw functions and events when necessary. Also can be used to create custom map image classes. Used within the MinecraftMediaLibrary to draw/display images to players.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void drawImage()
      Draws a specified image onto a Map.
      void onDrawImage()
      Called before image is drawn.
